ilog.concert

Interface IloIntRange

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IloDataCollection, IloDiscreteDataCollection, IloIntCollection

    public interface IloIntRange
extends IloIntCollection
    This interface represents the domain of an integer range. It can be enumerated using an iterator. It is represented by a lower bound and an upper bound.

    • Method Summary
